iend of Benoit Samuelson's, said.\", \"from\": 6010, \"to\": 6171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The neighbors\", \"from\": 6011, \"to\": 6024}, {\"ngram\": \"Adam\", \"from\": 6047, \"to\": 6051}, {\"ngram\": \"Eve\", \"from\": 6056, \"to\": 6059}, {\"ngram\": \"autographs\", \"from\": 6113, \"to\": 6123}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\" Hansen\", \"from\": 6124, \"to\": 6132}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 6134, \"to\": 6142}, {\"ngram\": \"Benoit Samuelson\", \"from\": 6146, \"to\": 6162}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After this, the argument that women did not belong in running-whether because of physical incapability, potential harm, or lack of interest-began to collapse.\", \"from\": 6173, \"to\": 6331, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the argument\", \"from\": 6185, \"to\": 6197}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 6203, \"to\": 6208}, {\"ngram\": \"running\", \"from\": 6227, \"to\": 6234}, {\"ngram\": \"physical incapability\", \"from\": 6254, \"to\": 6275}, {\"ngram\": \"potential harm\", \"from\": 6277, \"to\": 6291}, {\"ngram\": \"lack\", \"from\": 6296, \"to\": 6300}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 6304, \"to\": 6312}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The very next games, the IOC added a 10,000-meter race.\", \"from\": 6332, \"to\": 6387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6357, \"end\": 6360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.550377620479939e-36, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 10,000-meter race\", \"from\": 6367, \"to\": 6386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 1996, the 5,000-meter race replaced the 3,000-meter one.\", \"from\": 6388, \"to\": 6447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 5,000-meter race\", \"from\": 6397, \"to\": 6417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few 